text: Hello, firstly I love your contents. I have an chatbot project and I want him to read both my files and examine my mssql database, follow the instruction I entered in the code and give high-quality answers. By providing these, I want to design a quality chatbot based on RAG with history in the form of q&a. I would like to state that I can connect this code with Aws and use it for public.
